Unsigned64.name: Unsigned64
Unsigned64.description: A non-negative 64-bit bit integer, without counter semantics.

eqlStorageContainerTable.name: eqlStorageContainerTable
eqlStorageContainerTable.description: EqualLogic-Persistent StorageContainerTable. This table contains a list of Storage Containers in a group and their attributes. TimeoutCreate:60 TimeoutDelete:60

eqlStorageContainerEntry.name: eqlStorageContainerEntry
eqlStorageContainerEntry.description: An entry (row) containing Storage Container info.

eqlStorageContainerIndex.name: eqlStorageContainerIndex
eqlStorageContainerIndex.description: This field specifies a unique index for identifying a Storage Container.

eqlStorageContainerRowStatus.name: eqlStorageContainerRowStatus
eqlStorageContainerRowStatus.description: This field is used to indicate the status of the entry i.e. whether the entry is active or not.

eqlStorageContainerUuid.name: eqlStorageContainerUuid
eqlStorageContainerUuid.description: EQL-SECONDARY-KEY This field is for internal use only.It stores the UUID for the storage container. The UUID is generated by the system.

eqlStorageContainerName.name: eqlStorageContainerName
eqlStorageContainerName.description: This field specifies a user friendly name for a Storage Container. The name must be unique within a group. The name must not contain spaces or special characters. The name can be up to 64 characters in length. There is no default.

eqlStorageContainerLookupName.name: eqlStorageContainerLookupName
eqlStorageContainerLookupName.description: EQL-SECONDARY-KEY This field specifies a string-prepped version of the Storage Container name, used for lookups. The name must be unique within a group. The name must not contain spaces or special characters. The name can be up to 64 characters in length. There is no default.

eqlStorageContainerDescription.name: eqlStorageContainerDescription
eqlStorageContainerDescription.description: This field specifies a descriptive string that provides details about the storage container. The description can be up to 128 characters. There is no default value.

eqlStorageContainerLogicalLimit.name: eqlStorageContainerLogicalLimit
eqlStorageContainerLogicalLimit.description: This field specifies the Storage Container *logical* limit in MB. There is no default. It should be larger than the physical size, as configured for this Storage Container.

eqlStorageContainerStatisticsTable.name: eqlStorageContainerStatisticsTable
eqlStorageContainerStatisticsTable.description: EqualLogic-Dynamic StorageContainerStatisticsTable. This table contains the statistics of the storage containers within an EQL group.

eqlStorageContainerStatisticsEntry.name: eqlStorageContainerStatisticsEntry
eqlStorageContainerStatisticsEntry.description: An entry (row) containing Storage Container statistics.

eqlStorageContainerStatisticsLogicalUsed.name: eqlStorageContainerStatisticsLogicalUsed
eqlStorageContainerStatisticsLogicalUsed.description: This field specifies how many MB of Logical Space is is allocated from this Storage Container. This is a dynamic value, it is not Administrator settable.

eqlStorageContainerStatisticsLogicalFree.name: eqlStorageContainerStatisticsLogicalFree
eqlStorageContainerStatisticsLogicalFree.description: This field specifies how many MB of Logical Space is free within this Storage Container. This is a dynamic value, it is not Administrator settable.

eqlStorageContainerStatisticsPhysicalUse.name: eqlStorageContainerStatisticsPhysicalUsed
eqlStorageContainerStatisticsPhysicalUse.description: This field specifies how many MB of Physical Space is allocated from this Storage Container. This is a dynamic value, it is not Administrator settable.

eqlStorageContainerStatisticsPhysicalFre.name: eqlStorageContainerStatisticsPhysicalFree
eqlStorageContainerStatisticsPhysicalFre.description: This field specifies how many MB of Physical Space is free within this Storage Container. This is a dynamic value, it is not Administrator settable.

eqlStorageContainerStatisticsThinProvFre.name: eqlStorageContainerStatisticsThinProvFree
eqlStorageContainerStatisticsThinProvFre.description: This field specifies how many MB of the Thin Provision Reserved Physical Space is free within this Storage Container. This is a dynamic value, it is not Administrator setable.

eqlStorageContainerStatisticsVvolsBound.name: eqlStorageContainerStatisticsVvolsBound
eqlStorageContainerStatisticsVvolsBound.description: The value of this object represents number of vvols within the storage container that are bound.

eqlStorageContainerStatisticsSVCount.name: eqlStorageContainerStatisticsSVCount
eqlStorageContainerStatisticsSVCount.description: The value of this object represents number of shared volumes for this storage container.

eqlStorageContainerStatisticsSVSCount.name: eqlStorageContainerStatisticsSVSCount
eqlStorageContainerStatisticsSVSCount.description: The value of this object represents number of shared volume sets for this storage container.

eqlStorageContainerStatisticsThinProvisi.name: eqlStorageContainerStatisticsThinProvisioned
eqlStorageContainerStatisticsThinProvisi.description: Are the buckets in this Storage Container thin-provisioned.

eqlStorageContainerStatisticsVvolsOnline.name: eqlStorageContainerStatisticsVvolsOnline
eqlStorageContainerStatisticsVvolsOnline.description: The value of this object represents number of vvols within the storage container that are online.

eqlStorageBucketTable.name: eqlStorageBucketTable
eqlStorageBucketTable.description: EqualLogic-Persistent StorageBucket Table. This table contains a list of Storage Buckets in a group and their attributes. TimeoutCreate:60 TimeoutDelete:60

eqlStorageBucketEntry.name: eqlStorageBucketEntry
eqlStorageBucketEntry.description: An entry (row) containing Storage Bucket info.

eqlStorageBucketIndex.name: eqlStorageBucketIndex
eqlStorageBucketIndex.description: This field specifies a unique index for identifying a Storage Bucket.

eqlStorageBucketRowStatus.name: eqlStorageBucketRowStatus
eqlStorageBucketRowStatus.description: This field is used to indicate the status of this entry i.e. whether the entry is active or not.

eqlStorageBucketName.name: eqlStorageBucketName
eqlStorageBucketName.description: This field specifies a user friendly name for a Storage Bucket. The name must be unique within a group. The name must not contain spaces or special characters. The name can be up to 64 characters in length. There is no default.

eqlStorageBucketLookupName.name: eqlStorageBucketLookupName
eqlStorageBucketLookupName.description: EQL-SECONDARY-KEY This field specifies a string-prepped version of the Storage Bucket name, used for lookups. The name must be unique within a group. The name must not contain spaces or special characters. The name can be up to 64 characters in length. There is no default.

eqlStorageBucketUuid.name: eqlStorageBucketUuid
eqlStorageBucketUuid.description: This is the unique identifier for the Storage Bucket, used in interacting with IOM.

eqlStorageBucketPhysicalSize.name: eqlStorageBucketPhysicalSize
eqlStorageBucketPhysicalSize.description: This field specifies the Storage Bucket *physical* size in MB. There is no default. It will be rounded up to the nearest increment of one page (15MB). It should be smaller than the logical size, as configured for this Storage Bucket.

eqlStorageBucketThinProvision.name: eqlStorageBucketThinProvision
eqlStorageBucketThinProvision.description: This field specifies if the StorageBucket is enabled for Thin Provisioning.

eqlStorageBucketThinMinReserve.name: eqlStorageBucketThinMinReserve
eqlStorageBucketThinMinReserve.description: This field specifies the amount of pool free space that is currently reserved for this Thin Provisioned StorageBucket configured as a percentage of eqlStorageBucketPhysicalSize.

eqlStorageBucketThinMaxGrow.name: eqlStorageBucketThinMaxGrow
eqlStorageBucketThinMaxGrow.description: This field specifies the amount of pool space that the storage bucket can grow to within the pool. This field is configured as a percentage of eqlStorageBucketPhysicalSize.

eqlStorageBucketFreeWarnPercentage.name: eqlStorageBucketFreeWarnPercentage
eqlStorageBucketFreeWarnPercentage.description: This field is configured as a percentage of the eqlStorageBucketPhysicalSize for thick provisioned volumes, but as a percentage of eqlStorageBucketThinMaxGrow for thin provisioned volumes. It is expected that IOM will raise a warning when the bucket's free space reaches this value. For thin provisioned volumes, it is expected that if the bucket's containing pool reaches this threshold (in terms of free pages) the warning will also be issued.

eqlParentStorageContainerPointer.name: eqlParentStorageContainerPointer
eqlParentStorageContainerPointer.description: This field specifies the row in the Storage Container table of the parent Storage Container for this Storage Bucket. If this value is null then the Storage Bucket is unassigned.

eqlParentStoragePoolIndex.name: eqlParentStoragePoolIndex
eqlParentStoragePoolIndex.description: This field specifies the index of the Storage Pool in which the bucket is placed.

eqlStorageBucketDynamicConfigTable.name: eqlStorageBucketDynamicConfigTable
eqlStorageBucketDynamicConfigTable.description: EqualLogic-Persistent Table for storing in database the Storage Bucket attributes that can independently change. This table is owned by MgmtExec, and is read/written upon request of IOM.

eqlStorageBucketDynamicConfigEntry.name: eqlStorageBucketDynamicConfigEntry
eqlStorageBucketDynamicConfigEntry.description: An entry (row) containing status for Storage Bucket dynamic config. The values in this table are not user configurable.

eqlStorageBucketDynamicReservePages.name: eqlStorageBucketDynamicReservePages
eqlStorageBucketDynamicReservePages.description: This field specifies the amount of pool space that is currently reserved for this Storage Bucket. It is valid for both thick and thin provisioned buckets.

eqlStorageBucketFreeWarnInUsePageCount.name: eqlStorageBucketFreeWarnInUsePageCount
eqlStorageBucketFreeWarnInUsePageCount.description: This field specifies the number of Storage Bucket pages that were in use when the last free-warn event for the bucket was received from IOM. It is valid for both thick and thin provisioned buckets.

eqlStorageBucketMaxResvInUsePageCount.name: eqlStorageBucketMaxResvInUsePageCount
eqlStorageBucketMaxResvInUsePageCount.description: This field specifies the number of Storage Bucket pages that were in use when the last max-resv event for the bucket was received from IOM. It is valid for both thick and thin provisioned buckets.

eqlStorageBucketFreeWarnThresholdPageCou.name: eqlStorageBucketFreeWarnThresholdPageCount
eqlStorageBucketFreeWarnThresholdPageCou.description: This field holds the value of the free-warn-threshold page count as it was set when the last free-warn event for the bucket was received from IOM. It is valid for both thick and thin provisioned buckets.

eqlStorageBucketStatisticsTable.name: eqlStorageBucketStatisticsTable
eqlStorageBucketStatisticsTable.description: EqualLogic-Dynamic Storage StorageBucketStatisticsTable. This table contains the statistics of the storage buckets within a group.

eqlStorageBucketStatisticsEntry.name: eqlStorageBucketStatisticsEntry
eqlStorageBucketStatisticsEntry.description: An entry (row) containing Storage Bucket statistics.

eqlStorageBucketStatisticsPhysicalUsed.name: eqlStorageBucketStatisticsPhysicalUsed
eqlStorageBucketStatisticsPhysicalUsed.description: This field specifies how many MB of Physical Space is allocated from this Storage Bucket. This is a dynamic value, it is not Administrator settable.

eqlStorageBucketStatisticsPhysicalFree.name: eqlStorageBucketStatisticsPhysicalFree
eqlStorageBucketStatisticsPhysicalFree.description: This field specifies how many MB of Physical Space is free within this Storage Bucket. This is a dynamic value, it is not Administrator settable.

eqlStorageBucketStatisticsThinProvFree.name: eqlStorageBucketStatisticsThinProvFree
eqlStorageBucketStatisticsThinProvFree.description: This field specifies how many MB of the Thin Provision Minimum Reserve Physical Space is free within this Storage Bucket. This is a dynamic value, it is not Administrator settable.

eqlStorageBucketStatisticsVvolsBound.name: eqlStorageBucketStatisticsVvolsBound
eqlStorageBucketStatisticsVvolsBound.description: The value of this object represents number of vvols within the storage container that are bound.

eqlStorageBucketStatisticsSVCount.name: eqlStorageBucketStatisticsSVCount
eqlStorageBucketStatisticsSVCount.description: The value of this object represents number of shared volumes for this storage bucket.

eqlStorageBucketStatisticsSVSCount.name: eqlStorageBucketStatisticsSVSCount
eqlStorageBucketStatisticsSVSCount.description: The value of this object represents number of shared volume sets for this storage bucket.

eqlStorageBucketStatisticsVvolsOnline.name: eqlStorageBucketStatisticsVvolsOnline
eqlStorageBucketStatisticsVvolsOnline.description: The value of this object represents number of vvols within the storage container that are online.
